Google Translate:
Good afternoon Team.

Our DLP, produced by a client of AGUILA COMPAÑIA DE SEGUROS, has an issue for which we request advice on the following issue:

The disk inside the Apliance is at its maximum point_ 10 GB free of 50GB, so we need to know how to increase this Apliance disk?

our version is_ 5.9.4.0

Solution_Comment__c: Disabled alerts and asked custoemr to check smtp settings. Deleted mqueue-client and mailer + other adjustments to clear space.
